Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JOJO的奇妙冒險 前文回顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 老頭 有些不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方向錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.18,0:00:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像要去那座島
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在進入埃及前我要稍微繞點路 為了見某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對這趟旅途而言 他是至關重要的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至關重要的人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 這種地方會有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個島好像很小啊 是個無人島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實 喬斯達先生 你說的那個人真的住在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一個人住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他在印度的時候告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？是哪個他？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:00:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？在印度吃咖喱？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:28.49,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}そして、集いしスターダスト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:35.05,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}100年目の目醒めに呼ばれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:39.92,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}男たちは向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:45.55,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}時の砂を越えるJourney
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:51.68,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}鎖のよう連なる 絡み合う宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:51.68,OP_CH,NTP,440,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}カルマ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:57.90,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}白金で断つ運命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:57.90,OP_CH,NTP,0,200,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:57.90,OP_CH,NTP,200,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}さだめ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:01.71,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Stand up! Stand up! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.95,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}打ち込むのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:07.57,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}All right now All right now All right now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:11.06,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}誇りのBullet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.36,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Break you down Break you down Break you down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:22.25,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}拳放つ 聖なるヴィジョン Stand Proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:28.49,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百年沉睡的甦醒在召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:35.05,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星塵遙呼 相繼匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:39.92,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}男子漢一行已啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:45.55,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踏上穿越時間的沙漠之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:51.68,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宿命 如同一串錯綜連橫的枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:57.90,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}揮起白金斬斷命運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.95,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迸射而出的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:11.06,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是高傲的彈頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:22.25,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鐵拳百裂 神聖的幻象 Stand Proud!
